name: Your Insight Serves You Well
Lore: 'Luke knew that while the dark side was quicker and more seductive, eventually evil would turn on itself.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. Opponent''s Dark Jedi are defense value -1. Scanning Crew and 3,720 To 1 are canceled. You may place Effect in Lost Pile to take one [Endor] or [Death Star II] Effect that deploys for free into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)',
